We don't want to list out this event call back in intellisense in that component parameters.

Code:
`
    @code {
   
    [Parameter]
    private int Year { get; set; }

    [Parameter]
    private EventCallback<int> YearChanged { get; set; }
   }
`

The `YearChanged` Event dont need to be list out in intellisense in razor page.

